snippet.title: Duck Detective: The Secret Salami - Official Announcement Trailer | Wholesome Snack December 2023
snippet.description: Meet the Duck Detective, investigate and discover secrets, and prepare to solve the mystery in Duck Detective: The Secret Salami, an upcoming detective mystery game coming to PC in 2024. Check out the announcement trailer for Duck Detective: The Secret Salami for a peek at various characters and more.
